  "description": {
    "zh": "你好，士兵，记得你和Prapor是好友吧？如果你对他而言能称得上朋友的话……\n不扯闲话了，听好了，他需要一些帮助。我觉得他是这里最清楚塔科夫情况的人。所以我希望主动提供些帮助，他也接受了帮助。他现在需要一堆武器，其中大多数是上世纪40年代和50年代的老古董，我猜他真的很喜欢苏联武器吧？好吧，这也不奇怪。\n\n你能办到吗？我记得他还提到了一些俄罗斯军用口粮，我建议你也带上一些，以防万一。还有，确保你带来的枪不是坏的。祝你好运，士兵。",
    "en": "Hello soldier, you are a good friend of Prapor right? If you can even call yourself friends...\nWhatever, listen up, he needed some help. I just thought he seems like someone who knows best what is going on here in Tarkov. So I offered my help to him and he accepted, he needs a bunch of guns, most of them are really old ones from the 40s and 50s, I am guessing he really likes Soviet Weaponry? Well, I would not be shocked.\n\nCan you manage this? I think he also said something about Russian MRE Packs, I suggest that you bring a few, just in case. Oh and make sure not to bring broken guns. Good luck Soldier."
  },
